steps.html_instructions: Take the California 85 S exit on the left toward Gilroy

Turn left onto CA-152 E/E 10th St/E Pacheco Pass Rd
Continue to follow CA-152 E
Merge onto I-5 S via the ramp to Los Angeles
Keep right at the fork to continue on CA-58 E, follow signs for Stockdale Hwy/Mojave/Tehachapl
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-15 N/Las Vegas/I-40 and merge onto I-15 N

Keep right at the fork to continue on I-40 E, follow signs for Needles
Passing through Arizona, New Mexico, Texas
Entering Oklahoma

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-40 E/US-270 E, follow signs for Fort Smith
Continue to follow I-40 E
Entering Arkansas
Keep right at the fork to continue on US-65 S, follow signs for Interstate 30 W/Little Rock
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
